Introduction

E-seol, also known as J-DAY and Jaeyi, and formerly as Chiu, is a South Korean singer under EMMP Company. She is a member of the girl group I:mond.

Before her solo debut, she was a member of two pre-debut girl groups: X:in and MEP-C formed through Universe.

She debuted as a soloist on November 2, 2021, under the stage name J-DAY. She released the digital single “I Want To Love”.
